Package org.rapla.entities.domain

The main domain entities of rapla (reservations and resources) are located in this package.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Allocatable
    Objects that implement allocatable can be allocated by reservations.
    Appointment
    The basic building blocks of reservations.
    AppointmentFormater
    Formats the different appointment outputs.
    Period
    Most universities and schools are planning for fixed periods/terms rather than arbitrary dates.
    Permission
    New feature to restrict the access to allocatables on a per user/group basis.
    Repeating
    Encapsulates the repeating rule for an appointment.
    Reservation
    The Reservation interface is the central interface of Rapla.

Package org.rapla.entities.domain Description

The main domain entities of rapla (reservations and resources) are located in this package. Take a look for a good overview of the rapla api.
